text: Slaviša Stojanović (born 6 December 1969) is a former Slovenian footballer and manager. He is currently managing Red Star Belgrade in the Serbian SuperLiga. Stojanović has won the Slovenian PrvaLiga twice with Domžale. ==References== Category:Slovenian footballers Category:Slovenian football managers Category:1969 births Category:Living people
title: Slaviša Stojanovič
